## Base URL for development (required)
# Uncomment the line below when developing locally
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

## VITE_API_BASE_URL (required)

- **Description**: Base URL for all API requests
- **Format**: `https://<host>:<port>/api`
- **Example**: `https://localhost:8000/api`
- **Security**: Always use HTTPS, even in production and development if possible.
- **Note**: This variable is used by various components for dynamic API endpoint construction.